The parable of security and anesthetics
> It is dangerous to engage in unscientific discussions in search of [peace of mind]. The idea that the damage can be greater, so long as we reassure everyone, is the same idea as using [anesthetics] to only take away the pain when you get sick. That is dangerous because the disease can progress rapidly. It is important not to rely on such unscientific thinking.
